com.polarion.platform.jobs.spi

Class AbstractJobParameter

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.polarion.platform.jobs.spi.AbstractJobParameter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IJobDescriptor.IJobParameter
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ArrayJobParameter, BuildArtifactJobParameter, LocationJobParameter, PropertiesJobParameter, SimpleJobParameter

    public abstract class AbstractJobParameter
extends java.lang.Object
implements IJobDescriptor.IJobParameter
    Abstract IJobDescriptor.IJobParameter.

    Parameter is by default active and required, has no default value and no description.

    Allows to modify all values which are not protected by dynamic change.

    Version:
    $Revision$ $Date$
    Author:
    Stepan Roh, Polarion Software
